{"tid":1439344,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"而家主軸變左打民意戰啦，堅持去北角嘅同我入黎！","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:29:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T09:29:25.000Z","uid":158766,"like":73,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"c68bbb5a2bd4b0c0ea63b38c99b506f697507255","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"福建幫吹雞嘅種種跡像都顯示聽日北角開拖係甚囂塵上，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔係話驚左班大陸喱，更唔係要和理非主場</span></span>，但<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>政府而家擺明係主動打民意輿論戰</strong></span></strong></span>，所以<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地唔可以再一味向前衝，要一齊思考每一步會點左右成個運動嘅發展</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聽日實在冇必要去北角冒險，助攻黑警加分。</span></strong></span>諗下，前線去到北角，班大陸喱衝出去同前線互毆，之後黑警出場鎮壓集體打鬥，結局就係黑警加分，藍衫放晒，只得手足有損傷，<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">黑警係淺黃中立淺藍眼中就變左英雄，你地甘心輸左之前做咁多文宣工作先拎到嘅民意咩？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要知道，如果一個政黨嘅立場鮮明，路線清晰，基本上選民個pool裡面會有兩成鐵票，兩成票必定投對家，拉票係拉中間果六成選民，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">而家我地正正就係要同政府去爭呢六成，甚至只係四成嘅中間派去支持自己！</span></span><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>只要鞏固埋呢班人嘅立場，以後不論罷工、佔政總、港鐵跳閘或其他抗爭升級就有更多民意支持，更加名正言順。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n所以聽日唔想送分比對家就麻煩各位，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>港島東和理非，要衝就去SSP！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1pz15oE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1pz15oE.jpg&h=92775b57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea7175986f86d32d7014624a40d547271cc15722","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8cc8396b4ee6d8a027e47a21b1e04e9cc3476e52","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:41:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6d6eed3c3bfe42fea3e9edcc4adeda37ffc4306","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc4fad18f6cd6da23a5870d3ba8b36e704a7fe02","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:42:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e5e61cd1c7360a170747fb3327b78a9b3bf90131","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:42:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a663dec0355864e30c31da642a801b82cdd8878","tid":1439344,"uid":2123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e29048916d833aada3c9566ceed7926eb587d34","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:42:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89b6297c21dfacc1dc853085ba9066e8e04b4f39","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a32e9ee13a976d21fa778112fc22208171b38512","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"deb80c3119bc79ea7237230315eb5bb250e5683a","tid":1439344,"uid":295888,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:44:40.000Z","msg":"中國人DNA：欺善怕惡！<br />\n<br />\n遊行本身好和平，警察只要做返正常工作就得，你係2百萬遊行個次就知！<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記警察本應係保護香港市民啊！如果佢地夠膽係北角重演721...嘿嘿嘿。"},{"pid":"bf54ec7d8810f0bca6275cb08f53f095cff5e9fd","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c56472993eef93e4973028c9bb0b6224a03ed4d","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:46:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0119d24265dc6557e6f1c8ca270d312a81eff4d0","tid":143934