書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">逢星期五，日擺買！減少家庭支出</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"fdf835f943c2d34b42b3191e7bac80733f5863cd","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"deb80c3119bc79ea7237230315eb5bb250e5683a","tid":1439344,"uid":295888,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:44:40.000Z","msg":"中國人DNA：欺善怕惡！<br />\n<br />\n遊行本身好和平，警察只要做返正常工作就得，你係2百萬遊行個次就知！<br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記警察本應係保護香港市民啊！如果佢地夠膽係北角重演721...嘿嘿嘿。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:51:41.000Z","msg":"仲唔明？佢地實唔會比你重演，仲會衝埋出黎做英雄將兩邊一網打盡，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇睇內文</span></span>？"},{"pid":"66531ad7d10ff821803989921e5a45699c06edcd","tid":1439344,"uid":268660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:51:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3ed004825b30c41a29896a05d906b37f57bd324d","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:52:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"db0e48e82497f0a31c5dab4736045999864944bf","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:52:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a2e2a0d765822d6b5c72e125cf3ea279479af5ab","tid":1439344,"uid":158766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4251e8bde50fd6a12cf1e164270fdb7c9240434c","tid":1439344,"uid":38260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:54:18.000Z","msg":"人多就唔驚"},{"pid":"de5775812a543f72456daecd1466d1d766a80bf7","tid":1439344,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:54:32.000Z","msg":"會唔會唔好咁快決定好啲<br />\n睇埋今晚同聽朝形勢<br />\n或者預早講定幾種可能情況既應變策略<br />\n例如如果得少數福建幫就點點點<br />\n如果對方有刀又點點點"},{"pid":"e